OL,3,CClimber found guilty of manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter girlfriend froze to death on
OL,5,Cmountain
OL,7,FAn Austrian court has found a 37-year-
OL,8,Fold climber guilty of manslaughter
OL,9,Fafter his girlfriend died on the
OL,10,Fcountry's tallest mountain.
OL,12,FThe court in Innsbruck handed Thomas P
OL,13,Fa five-month suspended prison sentence
OL,14,Fand a fine of E9,600 (#8,400) for
OL,15,Fcausing the woman's death in January
OL,16,F2025 by gross negligence.
OL,18,FHis girlfriend, named Kerstin G, died
OL,19,Fof hypothermia during a climbing trip
OL,20,Fon Grossglockner mountain.
