OL,7,FThomas P pleaded not guilty, telling
OL,8,Fthe court he was "terribly sorry" and
OL,9,Fthat his girlfriend's death was a
OL,10,F"tragic accident".
OL,12,FIn January 2025, Thomas P and Kerstin
OL,13,FG were just 50 metres from the 3,798
OL,14,Fmetre summit of Grossglocker when she
OL,15,Fbegan to experience exhaustion and
OL,16,Fdisorientation, according to the
OL,17,FInnsbruck public prosecutor's office.
OL,19,FThe 33-year-old later froze to death
OL,20,Fafter Mr P left her at 2am on January
OL,21,F19.
