OL,7,FHe returned to the mountain some six
OL,8,Fand a half hours later to find her
OL,9,Fdead after descending the summit in
OL,10,Forder to find help, the public
OL,11,Fprosecutor says.
OL,13,FThe court heard that the woman had
OL,14,Fbecome exhausted and was unable to
OL,15,Fkeep going when they approached the
OL,16,Fsummit.
OL,18,FProsecutors say that he made a number
OL,19,Fof serious errors in planning and
OL,20,Fpartaking in the climb.
