OL,7,FWhile atop the mountain, Ms G was left
OL,8,Fin -8C conditions, but as winds picked
OL,9,Fup to around 45mph, temperatures could
OL,10,Fhave felt as low as -20C.
OL,12,FAn 11-month investigation has examined
OL,13,Fthe couple's mobile phones, sports
OL,14,Fwatches, photographs of their ascent,
OL,15,Fand an independent report from a
OL,16,Fmountaineering expert.
