OL,3,CClimber found guilty of manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter girlfriend froze to death on
OL,5,Cmountain
OL,7,FOne of the main allegations put to
OL,8,FThomas P concerned Kerstin G's
OL,9,Fequipment. Prosecutors argued that she
OL,10,Fhad been allowed to climb with a
OL,11,Fsplitboard and soft snowboard boots,
OL,12,Fboth of which were deemed unsuitable
OL,13,Ffor the climb.
OL,15,FThey also argued that the couple
OL,16,Fshould have turned back due to strong
OL,17,Fwinds and freezing temperatures.
