OL,7,FPolice attempted to call Mr P several
OL,8,Ftimes before he called an officer back
OL,9,Fat 12.35am. No further contact was
OL,10,Fmade, and the prosecutor's office said
OL,11,Fhis phone was placed on silent.
OL,13,FThe maximum sentence in the case was
OL,14,Fup to three years in prison. However,
OL,15,Fthe court imposed a five-month
OL,16,Fsentence, suspended for three years.
